 economist subscription required  stanley marcus july   the goldman sachs guide to manipulating commodities us news  world report   kocieniewski david august   us subpoenas goldman in inquiry of aluminum warehouses new york times   a b harris andrew december   goldman sachs aluminum antitrust suits shipped to nyc bloomberg lp   a b depillis lydia july   heres how goldman sachs is making your beer more expensive the washington post   lenzner robert july   goldman sachs makes  million storing  of global aluminum production forbes   levine matt november   the goldman sachs aluminum conspiracy was pretty silly bloomberg lp   berthelsen christian iosebashvili ira december   goldman sachs sells aluminum business to swiss firm the wall street journal subscription required  lef jonathan mason josephine lacapra lauren tara december   goldman sells metro metals warehouse unit to reuben bros reuters   popper nathaniel december   goldman sells aluminum subsidiary the new york times subscription required  a b sheppard kate september    gas brought to you by wall street mother jones   a b big banks bet crude oil prices would fall in  runup leaked data show bloomberg lp just before crude oil hit its record high in mid  of the worlds largest banks were betting that prices would fall according to private trading data released by us senator bernie sanders the net positions of the banks undermine arguments made by sanders that speculative trades on wall street drove oil prices in  said craig pirrong director of the global energy management institute at the university of houston retail gasoline reached a record  a gallon on july   and oil peaked at  a barrel on july  that year   a b johnson brad april   goldman sachs admits record speculation to blame for skyrocketing gas prices thinkprogress   a b sherter alain april   when goldman sachs warns that speculation drives oil prices listen up cbs news   a b c kennedy ii joseph p april   the high cost of gambling on oil the new york times  